==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tiānxià bĕn wúshì, yōngrénzìrăo zhī

===Etymology===
Literally: Nothing under the heavens is the matter until a person of mediocre ability messes things up for himself

===Idiom===
'''[[天下]][[本]][[無事]]，[[庸人自擾]][[之]]'''
# to not think things through, and thereby create unnecessary trouble for oneself; to try to fix something that was not broken in the first place
#: ''[[處女座]][[容易]][[陷入]]'''天下本無事庸人自擾之'''[[的]][[情緒]][[中]]，[[根本]][[都]][[沒有]][[什麼]][[事情]][[發生]]，[[心情]][[要]][[放]][[開]][[一點]][[不要]][[想]][[太多]]。''
#: ''Virgos will find it easy to fall into the trap of feeling like they should '''try to fix something that was not broken in the first place'''.  Nothing has actually happened, so relax and don't overthink things.''

===Alternate forms===
[[天下本无事，庸人自扰之]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])
